{"image_id": "AMZN_2004_page_86", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "AMAZON.COM, INC.", "bbox": [516.6, 140.2, 721.4, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [279.5, 177.7, 958.6, 198.5]}, {"text": "Note 8—OTHER OPERATING EXPENSE (INCOME)", "bbox": [143.8, 227.7, 636.6, 248.6]}, {"text": "Other operating expense (income) was $(8) million, $3 million, and $47 million for 2004, 2003, and 2002,", "bbox": [185.5, 264.3, 1074.3, 285.1]}, {"text": "which includes restructuring-related expenses (credits) and amortization of other intangibles. Restructuring-", "bbox": [143.8, 289.3, 1045.6, 310.1]}, {"text": "related expenses (credits) were $(9) million, $0 million, and $42 million; and amortization of other intangibles", "bbox": [143.8, 314.3, 1066.6, 335.1]}, {"text": "was $1 million, $3 million, and $5 million for 2004, 2003, and 2002.", "bbox": [143.8, 339.3, 718.3, 360.2]}, {"text": "During 2004, we determined that certain of the office space previously vacated as part of our 2001", "bbox": [185.5, 387.1, 1008.2, 408.0]}, {"text": "restructuring, which we had been unable to sublease due to poor real estate market conditions, was necessary for", "bbox": [143.8, 412.1, 1083.6, 433.0]}, {"text": "our future needs. We reduced our restructuring-related liability resulting in a gain of $13 million for 2004. Lease", "bbox": [143.8, 437.2, 1085.1, 458.0]}, {"text": "payments for this office space are expensed over the lease period and classified to the corresponding operating", "bbox": [143.8, 462.2, 1066.9, 483.0]}, {"text": "expense categories on the consolidated statements of operations.", "bbox": [143.8, 487.2, 681.8, 508.0]}, {"text": "In 2004, we streamlined our organizational structure in France to reduce our operating costs. These efforts", "bbox": [185.5, 535.0, 1073.1, 555.8]}, {"text": "were primarily focused on eliminating French-office positions in managerial, professional, clerical, and technical", "bbox": [143.8, 560.0, 1088.7, 580.8]}, {"text": "roles. The number of employees affected totaled 52 and resulted in severance costs of $4 million classified in", "bbox": [143.8, 585.0, 1056.7, 605.9]}, {"text": "“Other operating expense (income)” on the consolidated statements of operations.", "bbox": [143.8, 610.0, 827.9, 630.9]}, {"text": "Restructuring-related charges were as follows (in thousands):", "bbox": [185.5, 657.8, 698.0, 678.7]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [835.5, 688.9, 1022.7, 705.6]}, {"text": "2004", "bbox": [826.5, 713.9, 859.8, 730.6]}, {"text": "2003", "bbox": [916.0, 713.9, 949.3, 730.6]}, {"text": "2002", "bbox": [1002.0, 713.9, 1035.3, 730.6]}, {"text": "(in thousands)", "bbox": [878.5, 738.9, 979.8, 755.6]}, {"text": "Asset impairments . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 760.9, 774.6, 781.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [805.8, 760.9, 816.3, 781.7]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [849.3, 760.9, 870.1, 781.7]}, {"text": "$—", "bbox": [911.8, 760.9, 943.1, 781.7]}, {"text": "$ 1,182", "bbox": [984.8, 760.9, 1052.5, 781.7]}, {"text": "Continuing lease obligations . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 785.9, 774.6, 806.7]}, {"text": "(12,304)", "bbox": [816.3, 785.9, 887.4, 806.7]}, {"text": "140", "bbox": [922.2, 785.9, 953.5, 806.7]}, {"text": "39,563", "bbox": [995.2, 785.9, 1052.5, 806.7]}, {"text": "Termination benefits . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 810.9, 774.6, 831.8]}, {"text": "4,225", "bbox": [833.7, 810.9, 880.6, 831.8]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [922.2, 810.9, 943.1, 831.8]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1021.2, 810.9, 1042.1, 831.8]}, {"text": "Broker commissions, professional fees, and other miscellaneous", "bbox": [185.5, 835.9, 721.1, 856.8]}, {"text": "restructuring costs . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [206.3, 860.